    "title": "Senior Teacher - NIT Warangal - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at NIT Warangal. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Teacher to strengthen our Dhanbad-based team.\n\nAbout NIT Warangal:\nNIT Warangal is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NIT Warangal!",
